/>\n不按基本法、不經民選的香港&ldquo;特首&rdquo;林鄭，在全港人民奮起的反修例運動以來。製造警暴、喬裝燒砸、潑墨扯旗、栽贓反咬、與民為敵，將香港塗炭超過8個月+。<br />\n<br />\n在大陸人禍瘟疫來臨，繼續倒行逆施，據不關閉口岸，荒謬到自己不戴口罩也不許人民戴口罩。卻準備在港九新界到處設立隔離區，報復90%反對她的港人，這隻 畜牲已經瘋狂到無以復加。<br />\n<br />\n全港人民不論男女老幼，完全有必要用實際行動，抵制這禍港者的一切政令，即逢林鄭必反，堅持對抗直到這個荒謬無恥政府滅亡！<br />\n<br />\n季羨林基金會曾主席2020年2月9日"},{"pid":"05888979661f7311c8682035d602bc88a4ae8886","tid":1871540,"uid":47659,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T14:22:19.000Z","msg":"醫護一戰你已經知香港罷工唔work<br />\n仲有其他工會吹雞吹左2,3星期都未有時間表<br />\n林奠係屋企都笑死喇"},{"pid":"d3316ff942021e687ff3d11fe321f28082ccf999","tid":1871540,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T14:23:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dba81cf232d7ab929da04ba2e3f36a42afa52e16","tid":1871540,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T14:24:06.000Z","msg":"入嚟推你班仆街"},{"pid":"1e13ecb5412a41ebdb1843c0c0de14e7b38a64e9","tid":1871540,"uid":42037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"05888979661f7311c8682035d602bc88a4ae8886","tid":1871540,"uid":47659,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T14:22:19.000Z","msg":"醫護一戰你已經知香港罷工唔work<br />\n仲有其他工會吹雞吹左2,3星期都未有時間表<br />\n林奠係屋企都笑死喇"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T14:24:33.000Z","msg":"兩個星期 thx"},{"pid":"a4e84562a58faf6effb30ef7e22b649321cc6144","tid":1871540,"uid":42037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T14:26:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2621862d14d4bea10365234baa85ebae5bc6f356","tid":1871540,"uid":9838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-09T14:34:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a0ea91c3ba7ce575cfacb004e02032a92aa71db","tid":1871540,"uid":983